<body>
    <h1>Updates to Add Category Component on the PB Retailer &amp; Influenc=
er</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Add the 'Add Category' action button and Add Category functionality on M=
obile layout</p></li>
<li>
<p>Add the Category component on the PB - business division Accounts (PB Re=
tailers &amp; Influencers) needs to be updated to remove =E2=80=98Search se=
llers option' as this option/field is not shown on the 'Edit Category compo=
nent=E2=80=99</p></li>
</ol>
